label: archegoniophore
definition: A specialized archegonial-bearing branch; the female gamentangiophore

label: antheridiophore
definition: A specialized antheridium-bearing branch; the male gamentangiophore

label: antheridium
definition: Male gametangium; a multicellular globose to broadly cylindric, stalked structure containing spermatozoides

label: archegonium
definition: Female gametangium; a multicellular, flask-shaped structure consisting of a stalk, venter, neck and containing an ovum

label: gemma cup
definition: Cup or moon-shaped, gemmae-containing structure of thalline or foliar origin

label: thallus
definition: A more of less flattened, gametophyte, not differentiated into a stem and leaves

label: sporophyte
definition: The spore-bearing new generation; initiated by the fertilization of an egg; remaining attached to the gametophyte and partially dependent on it
notes: Typically consisting of foot, seta, and capsule
